00:48:29,225 --> 00:48:32,527
This relates directly to Agile, and this

894
00:48:32,527 --> 00:48:35,610
is around understanding the situation that you're in.

895
00:48:35,610 --> 00:48:38,613
Situational awareness, and then having a measured response

896
00:48:38,613 --> 00:48:40,514
to the situation that you're in.

897
00:48:40,514 --> 00:48:43,557
To go from being a good producer to a great producer,

898
00:48:43,557 --> 00:48:45,598
this is something that you have to master,

899
00:48:45,598 --> 00:48:48,281
is modifying your approach to the situation

900
00:48:48,281 --> 00:48:50,042
that you're in with your project and your team.

901
00:48:52,705 --> 00:48:55,928
And hand in hand with that practiced agility.

902
00:48:55,928 --> 00:49:00,453
So, you know, how many of you now are kind of in full

