00:49:00,453 --> 00:49:03,516
or very heavily adopted agile production frameworks

904
00:49:03,516 --> 00:49:03,797
in your studio?

905
00:49:03,797 --> 00:49:07,441
Okay, not everyone, but many, most of you I'd say.

906
00:49:08,624 --> 00:49:15,011
I found, and you probably know, I haven't found a common implementation of Agile or

