00:50:13,911 --> 00:50:16,473
but being able to identify your strengths, weaknesses,

922
00:50:16,473 --> 00:50:17,914
opportunities, and threats.

923
00:50:17,914 --> 00:50:21,297
But being able to then use that as a way to explain

924
00:50:21,297 --> 00:50:23,439
to other, say, executive stakeholders,

