00:50:23,439 --> 00:50:26,181
or even people on the team, what kinds of things

926
00:50:26,181 --> 00:50:27,703
you should pursue in your projects,

927
00:50:27,703 --> 00:50:30,045
or people you should hire, especially if you're doing

928
00:50:30,045 --> 00:50:32,387
gap analysis for your teams, to be able to use that

929
00:50:32,387 --> 00:50:34,709
as a way to describe how you came to those answers

