00:50:46,304 --> 00:50:53,808
be a super producer in the industry, you need to be able to lead people into innovation.

933
00:50:53,808 --> 00:50:59,591
You can't just be standing behind waiting for others as they're making decisions to

934
00:50:59,591 --> 00:51:03,854
try to pick up the pieces from them to see how you can support the efforts that they

935
00:51:03,854 --> 00:51:04,254
want.

